description	"Chef Cyborg

^2Weaponry:
- Lightsaber
-- ^4Blue ^7Style Only
- Advanced Flamethrower ^3[CS2]

^8Attributes:
- Cortosis (1)
- Melee Resistance
- View Ally Stats
- Speed Boost [Speed 3]
- Fuel (3)

These Chef Cyborgs use their specially made lightsabers to cut up brains and make burger slices out of them and the corpses that they often get in from the graveyard diggers.
These units are no match against darth vader and they rely solely on the 'spammy spam spam' skill that Reaper MacZombie taught them in order to kill peices of dead corpse meat.
They also have the ability to cook meat manually, although they often prefer to use them as weapons, such as burning off people's skin. Another work-grown talent is the ability to speed up when demand increases, this is also a useful weapon for surprising the enemy.
Also, these units have gotten used to MacZombie's constant gripping of them when they fail a task, so Vader's grip will be useless against this units unless they let their guard down."